      "Text": {
        "TableId": "/Game/UI/MainMenu/ST_MainMenus.ST_MainMenus",
        "Key": "ui.mainmenus.landing.newsfeed.Body",
        "SourceString": "We're delighted to have you on this journey with us. Pardon our dust: the project is in early access, so you may encounter bugs or issues during your time in-game. Balancing and content is not yet final.\r\n\r\nWe want to hear from you! We’ve got a range of social channels, including our Discord where we’ll be using community feedback to inform the future roadmap of the game. We’re always on the lookout for feedback, so stay tuned for more updates! Until then, have fun!\r\n\r\n– The RuneScape: Dragonwilds Team",
        "LocalizedString": "We're delighted to have you on this journey with us. Pardon our dust: the project is in early access, so you may encounter bugs or issues during your time in-game. Balancing and content is not yet final.\r\n\r\nWe want to hear from you! We’ve got a range of social channels, including our Discord where we’ll be using community feedback to inform the future roadmap of the game. We’re always on the lookout for feedback, so stay tuned for more updates! Until then, have fun!\r\n\r\n– The RuneScape: Dragonwilds Team"
      },
